@node Merge mode
@chapter Merge mode

@code{gdocs-merge-mode} is a major mode derived from @code{special-mode} used in
the @samp{*gdocs-merge*} buffer during conflict resolution.  Its keybindings
are documented in @ref{Conflict resolution (1), , Conflict resolution}.

The mode defines three faces for visual differentiation:

@itemize
@item
@code{gdocs-merge-local-face} (green background) for local changes.
@item
@code{gdocs-merge-remote-face} (red background) for remote changes.
@item
@code{gdocs-merge-resolved-face} (blue background) for resolved hunks.
@end itemize

